7 CONCLUSIONS AND FUTURE WORK :
7-1:In this paper, we have explored how to exploit implicit feedback information, including query history and clickthrough history within the same search session, to improve information retrieval performance .
7-2:Using the KL divergence retrieval model as the basis, we proposed and studied four statistical language models for context sensitive information retrieval, i.e., FixInt, BayesInt, OnlineUp and BatchUp .
